info.name: Biscoff Bomb
info.description: Indulge in a Biscoff explosion! Our crispy waff-wich is a masterpiece layered with Lotus Biscoff spread, crowned with delectable Lotus Biscoff ice cream, sprinkled with crumbs, and adorned with a drizzle of melted white chocolate and extra Biscoff spread. It's a Biscoff lover's dream!

info.name: Death By Chocolate
info.description: Dive into our signature chocolate waff-wich, layered with milk chocolate spread topped with hot chocolate fudge, choco chips, Oreos, Kit Kat, and rich creamy chocolate ice cream. It's a breath-stealing blend of pure indulgence!

info.name: Mint Choco Chip
info.description: A lovestory like never before. Our signature black velvet waff-wich, layered with hot chocolate fudge, topped with milk & white chocolate spread,  choco chips & the unqiue  "Mint choco chip" ice cream- A lovestory that transcends the ordinary.

info.name: Berry-Nana Caramel Swirl
info.description: A wonderland of flavours. Our classic crispy waff-wich layered with milk chocolate topped with strawberry banana ice cream with a swirl of caramel sauce, salted caramel popcorn, roasted almond & bananas. Pure indulgence in every bite!

info.name: KitKat Affair
info.description: Make the most of this Affair.  Our crispy classic waff-wich is a masterpiece layered with melted Belgian white chocolate topped with creamy vanilla ice cream, KitKat crumbs & drizzled with melted Belgian white and milk chocolate. For KitKat lovers!

info.name: Nutella Overload
info.description: Unleash the mighty flavour with our crispy classic waff-wich layered in Nutella, crowned with vanilla ice cream, and topped with melted Belgian white chocolate, Nutella spread, roasted almonds, and a playful wafer roll. It's a taste revolution!

info.name: Kiki Monster
info.description: Savor pure decadence with our Black Velvet waff-wich, layered with Kiki & Cream filling, topped with Cookie & Cream ice cream, hot chocolate fudge, melted Belgian white chocolate, and Oreo crumbs. Dessert perfection in every bite!

info.name: Almond Fudge Brownie
info.description: Epitome of indulgence in a single bite:  A waff-wich And A Brownie. Layered with the goodness of Nutella & topped with hot chocolate fudge, roasted almond, wafer roll & creamy vanilla ice cream- a symphony of flavors that unites the best of both worlds.
